manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/bin/client.rs"
name = "client"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/bin/server.rs"
name = "server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "pow_challenge_server_http"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
dashmap = "5.5.3"
hex = "0.4.3"
jsonwebtoken = "8.0"
once_cell = "1.8"
rand = "0.8.4"
serde_json = "1.0"
sha2 = "0.10.8"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1.0.79"
features = ["backtrace"]

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7.4"
features = ["http2"]

[dependencies.axum-extra]
version = "0.9.2"
features = ["typed-header"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.24"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "pow_challenge_server_http_lib"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []
